meta.description: Kim Mack Rosenberg is a lawyer in private practice in New York City. Her practice focuses on insurance coverage and related litigation as well as products liability. She is a co-author of "The HPV Vaccine on Trial: Seeking Justice for a Generation Betrayed." She also serves in leadership positions with several non-profits concerned with issues regarding children’s health.
